{"tid":2445080,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁卓偉：德國BioNTech疫苗較適合常到歐美等地的人士 常到中国的人士不用考慮","createTime":"2021-03-13T10:40:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T10:48:58.000Z","uid":212626,"like":12,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1ad75fddb7a4c954532e5aa0d99ef3d74a95099b","tid":2445080,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T10:40:00.000Z","msg":"梁卓偉表示，本港大部分接種新冠疫苗後須送往深切治療部，甚至死亡個案，都是與心血管疾病，尤其是栓塞有關。他認為，如果制訂清晰和具體的接種指引，列明反映人體狀態的指標，例如血壓和血糖水平等，能令醫護較容易跟進個案，但強調長期病患者最好向家庭醫生查詢病情是否受控、是否適合接種疫苗。 <br />\n<br />\n梁卓偉又說，市民選擇打哪款新冠疫苗屬個人決定，德國BioNTech(復必泰)疫苗的臨床測試已證實對英國變種病毒有效，時常要到歐美等地的人士可能較有效；相反，常到內地的人士，就可能無相關考慮。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2382806\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2382806&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfEXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=703cc719\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2382806</a>"},{"pid":"8aaefff2005850314118f55a5d0f4089659edc32","tid":2445080,"uid":376274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T10:40:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af4f9cf9652b5a5d5ae8c43048b0072f5a3b873f","tid":2445080,"uid":29675,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T10:41:54.000Z","msg":"常到內地的人士，就可能無相關考慮。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CNFTEBV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCNFTEBV.jpg&h=238a5a7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a000deb9824e05ba24769fee24acb603b4ba9779","tid":2445080,"uid":260251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T10:42:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c54fe75bd217c951bfab8856378a21ea30296c9","tid":2445080,"uid":325346,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T10:42:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講到英國變種病毒唔會傳到中國咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f3e2a88cc7ea295bf9744dfb79b39452b652804","tid":2445080,"uid":69841,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T10:42:17.000Z","msg":"中國邊有疫情<br />\n梁卓偉係咪發布不實言論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1a271f1e5a3f81ad9c01b7e0ad3eb59487c0850","tid":2445080,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8f3e2a88cc7ea295bf9744dfb79b39452b652804","tid":2445080,"uid":69841,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T10:42:17.000Z","msg":"中國邊有疫情<br />\n梁卓偉係咪發布不實言論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T10:42:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41e546d503bcd7f8e510a7820acec8779311a199","tid":2445080,"uid":41873,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T10:42:50.000Z","msg":"講咁多 一句講哂 政府係唔會負責 人命賤過地底泥 講完"},{"pid":"5081a646fb1ac3d87ba69b6f3374553c677da329","tid":2445080,"uid":361751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T10:42:52.000Z","msg":"藝人黃夏蕙本周一（8日）因膝蓋舊患看診所醫生，同日在她沒有跟親友討論下，醫生遊說她即時接種科興疫苗。接種疫苗後，黃夏蕙的家人均擔心她身體是否負荷得了，不時聯絡及問候。本來沒太大擔心的她亦有所懷疑，曾向親友查問，「係唔係要打埋另一款針（復必泰疫苗）可能安全返啲？」家人正遊說她不要重複接種疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d419525ef87d2e754338cc1c30603cf04e1dc6a8","tid":2445080,"uid":52876,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T10:44:05.000Z","msg":"講咁多, 即係biontech可以防埋英國變種,&nbsp;支那科興唔得"},{"pid":"f0f7cec0005e3713d16f73cebef28b5ce332c7a6","tid":2445080,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af4f9cf9652b5a5d5ae8c43048b0072f5a3b873f","tid":2445080,"uid":29675,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T10:41:54.000Z","msg":"常到內地的人士，就可能無相關考慮。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CNFTEBV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCNFTEBV.jpg&h=238a5a7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T10:44:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea2992d9a7722c760c84a15274be69984190572e","tid":2445080,"uid":152636,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T10:45:54.000Z","msg":"梁卓偉︰時常要到歐美等地的人士可能較有效<br />\n鈕祜祿︰今日有4宗為輸入個案，均帶有N501Y變種病毒株<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b766545338b885c006dc531200ae856ec7a620f8","tid":2445080,"uid":276273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T10:48:52.000Z","msg":"乜D紀律部隊唔去中國，要去歐洲咩，<br />\n上星期有6個部隊都去打 BioNTech, 係咪佢哋令去歐洲，都唔去中國呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87b970a2e73f66b53f28ae870a58885d6e4f7f51","tid":2445080,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T10:48:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}